N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 107.4 - Use of the terms "shall" and "may"
State Regulations

As used in this Subchapter, the term shall denotes a
mandatory meaning and the term may denotes a permissive
meaning. Notes
